Package: facetext2
Title: Easy Text Annotation for ggplot2 Faceted Plots
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("JK", "Kim", , "kimjk@agronomy4future.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides two helper functions for adding text annotations 
    (e.g. significance labels, group letters) to ggplot2 faceted plots 
    using relative coordinates (0 to 1). facetext() supports single-variable 
    faceted plots created with facet_wrap(), and facetext2() supports 
    two-variable faceted plots created with facet_grid().
